kernel_variant.question:
Compute
\[
\Lambda \;=\;
\log_{2}\Biggl(\;
        \prod_{a=1}^{5005}
        \;\prod_{b=1}^{5005}
        \;\prod_{c=1}^{5005}
        \Bigl(1+\exp\!\bigl[\tfrac{2\pi i}{5005}\,abc\bigr]\Bigr)
      \Biggr),
\]
where \(i^{2}=-1\) and \(5005=5\cdot7\cdot11\cdot13\).

